summary: A small dungeon for mid-to-high players.
descriptionHtml:
Just south of Riverwood lies a small house, abandoned for years after its owner\'s mysterious disappearance. Some say it was due to bandits. Others, that a ruin was found beneath the foundation of the dwelling, and the undead neighbors were not very friendly. And a smaller, quieter rumor, speaks of an Empress long thought dead, waiting for her moment to strike. 

Technical Details - 

A very small dungeon mod with high-level enemies, and a unique set of Daedric Armor. Should be compatible with pretty much everything, but if there are any mod conflicts be sure to let me know.
author: Karkashan
